Installing OCR
For CPU:
pip install paddlepaddle
pip install paddleocr

For GPU:
PaddleOCR install (select CUDA version): https://www.paddlepaddle.org.cn/en/install/quick?docurl=/documentation/docs/en/develop/install/pip/windows-pip_en.html
Then use "pip install paddleocr" in cmd

Installing NER
Run: spacy download en_core_web_trf